Hi! This folder contain all the production notes that you need if you wanted to print this in JLCPCB
FIrst, there is the gerber zip files which contain all the gerber files that you need to summon the 3D looks of this dev board.
Then there is also the BOM and POS file that you need to input if you want to do a PCBA / PCB Assembly
If you don't do the PCBA you need to buy the part separated and then handsolder it
